  Usage : The program will show 'graphically' the amount of free
  ÄÄÄÄÄ   disk and memory space. Call the program with

          DMI [Drive] [/M]

          Drive is the disk drive for which you want information
          /M will force monocrome display on a color/composite monitor. It
             will check if you have a color or monocrome monitor.


  Info  : The program will display info about
  ÄÄÄÄ
          - Total disk space
          - Used free disk space
          - Available disk space (pure arithmetic !!!)
          - Total RAM
          - Used RAM
          - Available RAM (see above !!!)
          - Initial extended memory
          - total expanded memory
          - available expanded memory


  Files : DMI.EXE  -  the executable program
  ÄÄÄÄÄ   DMI.PAS  -  the Pascal 5.5 source code
